        BAD_IS_WAR_SUFFERING_WAR_BRINGS_NO_MORE                                       = 8680,  -- Bad, is war. Suffering, war brings. No more, we fight.
        THE_MOMENT_I_HEARD_THOSE_WORDS_IT_WAS                                         = 8681,  -- The moment I heard those words it was as if a dark cloud had been lifted from my heart. Maybe we can put an end to it, I thought.
