        THERE_S_A_PLACE_BENEATH_THE_WAJAOM_WOODLANDS                                  = 8907,  -- There's a place beneath the Wajaom Woodlands--an expansive network of caves known as the Aydeewa Subterrane. If you went in there without a map, you'd never come out...
