        AH_MISTER_MISS_THE_BOSS_HAS_RETIRED_FOR                                       = 8919,  -- Ah, Mister/Miss] %. The boss has retired for the day. He won't wake up, even if Al Zahbi comes under attack from the beastmen. He's not easily excited...
