        BLUE_MAGIC_IS_A_POWERFUL_FORCE_IT_PLACES                                      = 8995,  -- Blue magic is a powerful force. It places an enormous stress on the body of the practitioner. You've been accepted into the Immortals--I'm sure you understand what that means.
