        AND_WHAT_ABOUT_MY_FEELINGS_ARE_YOU_SAYING                                     = 12771,  -- And what about my feelings!? Are you saying that I'm too weak to find a way to break a measly frog curse on my own? Well, bring it on, I say!
        IF_YOU_D_LIKE_TO_KNOW_I_VE                                                    = 12772,  -- If you'd like to know, I've been spending the last eight days practicing on how to act once I'm transformed. So there!
