        A_FINE_PIECE_OF_PHOTOGRAPHY_YOU_HAVE_MY                                       = 13183,  -- A fine piece of photography! You have my thanks!
        HMMM_SURELY_YOU_CAN_DO_BETTER_THAN_THIS                                       = 13184,  -- Hmmm... Surely you can do better than this, my friend. But I will accept it nevertheless.
        WHY_THIS_IS_SO_YOU_WERE_SUCCESSFUL_IN                                         = 13185,  -- Why, this is...! So you were successful in subduing the creature? You are indeed an adventurer worthy of admiration!
        PLEASE_ACCEPT_THIS_FAR_EASTERN_TALLY_SEAL_AS                                  = 13186,  -- Please accept this Far Eastern tally seal as a symbol of my faith in you.
        A_SINGLE_TALLY_SEAL_IS_PROOF_POSITIVE_OF                                      = 13187,  -- A single tally seal is proof positive of your prowess as an adventurer. You shan't be requiring another.
        AH_PLEASE_FORGIVE_ME_MY_MASTER_SANRAKU_WHOM                                   = 13188,  -- Ah, please forgive me. My master, Sanraku, whom I respect and revere, has forbidden me from engaging in conversation, as it will disrupt my attunement with nature.
        GREETINGS_ADVENTURER_MY_NAME_IS_RYO_APPRENTICE_TO                             = 13189,  -- Greetings, adventurer. My name is Ryo, apprentice to Master Sanraku. The master has instructed me to assist you in whatever way possible.
        GOOD_DAY_HOW_MAY_I_BE_OF_SERVICE                                              = 13190,  -- Good day, %. How may I be of service?
        WHAT_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_ASK_ABOUT_WHAT                                         = 13191,  -- What would you like to ask about? What's zeni? My zeni balance. Sanraku's subject of interest. Recommended fauna. The criteria for a good image. Far Eastern tally seals. Obtaining a soultrapper. Getting access to islets. Nothing.
        YOU_CURRENTLY_HAVE_ZENI_IN_YOUR_ACCOUNT                                       = 13192,  -- You currently have # zeni in your account.
        AH_YES_ZENI_THIS_MAY_REQUIRE_SOME_EXPLAINING                                  = 13193,  -- Ah yes, zeni... This may require some explaining. A keen eye and peerless attention to detail are attributes that made Master Sanraku the artistic genius that he is. The very same things, however, have also given him a somewhat calculating personality.
        TAKE_ZENI_THE_FAR_EASTERN_CURRENCY_FOR_EXAMPLE                                = 13194,  -- Take zeni, the Far Eastern currency, for example. This is Master Sanraku's way of keeping track of your contribution to his objectives.
        BRINGING_HIM_A_SOUL_PLATE_IMAGE_OF_FAUNA                                      = 13195,  -- Bringing him a soul plate image of fauna will earn you virtual zeni in your account. For your information, the account keeper is me.
        ON_THE_OTHER_HAND_MASTER_SANRAKU_WILL_DEDUCT                                  = 13196,  -- On the other hand, Master Sanraku will deduct zeni from your account as a fee for providing information on fauna.
        WHILE_I_DO_NOT_ENTIRELY_AGREE_TO_MASTER                                       = 13197,  -- While I do not entirely agree to Master's cumbersome methodology, as a mere apprentice it is not my place to make comments.
        THIS_GOES_WITHOUT_SAYING_BUT_THE_SUBJECT_MUST                                 = 13198,  -- This goes without saying, but the subject must be well framed in the shot.
        AND_PREFERABLY_BE_OF_A_CREATURE_IN_WHICH                                      = 13199,  -- And preferably, be of a creature in which Master is interested.
        HOWEVER_LIKE_HIS_INABILITY_TO_STAY_FAITHFUL_TO                                = 13200,  -- However, like his inability to stay faithful to one woman, his subject of interest is also prone to change.
        ONE_LAST_THING_IF_YOU_SHOW_ME_YOUR                                            = 13201,  -- One last thing. If you show me your soul plates before giving them to the master, I can give you an estimate on their worth in zeni.
        THE_PURSUIT_OF_BEAUTY_IN_NATURE_IS_OFTEN                                      = 13202,  -- The pursuit of beauty in nature is often accompanied by unavoidable hazards. There are times when one has no choice but to slay an aggravated creature in self-defense.
        WHEN_YOU_DEFEAT_SUCH_A_CREATURE_BRING_BACK                                    = 13203,  -- When you defeat such a creature, bring back evidence of your feat to show to Master Sanraku.
        FROM_HIS_NUMEROUS_JOURNEYS_ACROSS_THE_GLOBE_MASTER                            = 13204,  -- From his numerous journeys across the globe, Master Sanraku has come to admire the courage and honor displayed by adventurers.
        IF_YOU_CAN_PROVE_YOUR_TRIUMPH_OVER_A                                          = 13205,  -- If you can prove your triumph over a formidable foe, the master will be pleased and reward you with a tally seal from the Far East.
        CONSIDER_IT_A_SYMBOL_OF_HIS_FAITH_IN                                          = 13206,  -- Consider it a symbol of his faith in your ability. Please note, however, that it isn't just for show. There is nothing for which Master Sanraku does not have a purpose.
        IN_THE_WAJAOM_WOODLANDS_MOUNT_ZHAYOLM_AND_CAEDARVA                            = 13207,  -- In the Wajaom Woodlands, Mount Zhayolm, and Caedarva Mire, you will find strange stone tablets that emit a soft glow from their engravings. These objects are thought to be a legacy of a long lost ancient civilization.
        LEGEND_SAYS_THAT_SPRINKLING_SALT_ONTO_THESE_TABLETS                           = 13208,  -- Legend says that sprinkling salt onto these tablets will teleport you to mystical islets.
        BEING_A_SKEPTIC_AT_HEART_MASTER_SANRAKU_COULDN                                = 13209,  -- Being a skeptic at heart, Master Sanraku couldn't resist the temptation to put this legend to the test, which he verified as fact.
        UPON_HIS_RETURN_HE_RANTED_ON_FOR_WEEKS                                        = 13210,  -- Upon his return, he ranted on for weeks on end about the rare fauna he witnessed on these islets, like a young boy who had seen an airship for the first time.
        I_RECALL_MASTER_SANRAKU_USING_SOME_VARIETY_OF                                 = 13211,  -- I recall Master Sanraku using some variety of sea salt.
        UNFORTUNATELY_I_HAVEN_T_YET_HAD_THE_PRIVILEGE                                 = 13212,  -- Unfortunately, I haven't yet had the privilege of seeing the islets with my own eyes.
        BUT_MASTER_SANRAKU_WILL_UNDOUBTEDLY_BE_PLEASED_TO                             = 13213,  -- But Master Sanraku will undoubtedly be pleased to have the opportunity to tell someone about his experience.
        YOU_CAN_OBTAIN_A_SOULTRAPPER_BY_GOING_TO                                      = 13214,  -- You can obtain a soultrapper by going to the Colosseum in the southeast area and speaking with a man named Zandjarl.
        IS_THERE_ANYTHING_ELSE_WITH_WHICH_I_CAN                                       = 13215,  -- Is there anything else with which I can assist?
        PLEASE_DO_NOT_HESITATE_TO_ASK_ME_IF                                           = 13216,  -- Please do not hesitate to ask me if there is anything you wish to know.
        YOU_VE_BROUGHT_ME_A_SOUL_PLATE_FOR                                            = 13217,  -- You've brought me a soul plate for appraisal?
        HMMM_YES_I_SEE                                                                = 13218,  -- Hmmm... Yes, I see...
        THIS_SAMPLE_SHOULD_EARN_YOU_APPROXIMATELY_ZENI                                = 13219,  -- This sample should earn you approximately # zeni.
