        HI_THERE_TOMCAT_PUSSYCAT                                                      = 14245,  -- Hi there, tomcat/pussycat].
        YOU_LOOK_TRRRUSTWORTHY_ENOUGH_GOT_A_MINUTE_TO                                 = 14246,  -- You look trrrustworthy enough. Got a minute to spare?
        BP7_7_H_LISTEN_TO_HER_I_LIKE                                                  = 14247,  -- bp7+\7)H Listen to her? I like where this is going. Get me away from her!
        DID_I_RRRUB_YOU_THE_WRONG_WAY_OH                                              = 14248,  -- Did I rrrub you the wrong way? Oh well, come back when you set your fur straight.
        WANT_ME_TO_WHISPURRR_SOME_SWEET_NOTHINGS_IN                                   = 14249,  -- Want me to whispurrr some sweet nothings in your ear?
        THAT_S_THE_ARRRDOR_I_WAS_LOOKING_FOR                                          = 14250,  -- That's the arrrdor I was looking for!
        THEN_IT_S_TIME_TO_TALK_ABOUT_THE                                              = 14251,  -- Then it's time to talk about the undersea rrruins of Alzadaal that lie at the western edge of the Arrradjiah Continent. In other words, around here. Stop me if you've already heard about it and the rrremnants that dot the landscapes within.
        DO_YOU_KNOW_OF_THE_REMNANTS_YES_SO                                            = 14252,  -- Do you know of the remnants? Yes, so stop right there. No, please tell me more.
        THAT_S_EXACTLY_WHAT_I_WANTED_TO_HEAR                                          = 14253,  -- That's exactly what I wanted to hear! (My eyes, they're grrreat at picking out capable adventurers.)
        NO_HAVE_YOU_BEEN_LIVING_UNDER_A_RRROCK                                        = 14254,  -- No...? Have you been living under a rrrock all these years!? (I can't believe my eyes would fail me for this fool.)
        LET_S_GET_YOU_UP_TO_SPEED_BEFORE                                              = 14255,  -- Let's get you up to speed before you become a cat's paw. There are four remnants within the Ruins of Alzadaal: Zhayolm, Arrapago, Bhaflau, and Silver Sea.
        SOME_FAT_CATS_THOUGHT_THEY_COLLECTED_ALL_THEY                                 = 14256,  -- Some fat cats thought they collected all they could long ago and abandoned the rrremnants, but there's still lots more to salvage down there.
        HERE_S_AN_EXAMPLE_OF_WHAT_YOU_CAN                                             = 14257,  -- Here's an example of what you can dig up in the rrruins. I'd been searrrching all over the realm for it!
        I_LIKE_YOUR_FACE_LOVERBOY_PRETTY_GIRL_SO                                      = 14258,  -- I like your face, loverboy/pretty girl], so I'll let you in on a little secret. People have found certain pieces of equipment that rrresonate with these artifacts. If you find any, show them to me and I'll sweeten your kitty.
        OH_BUT_LET_S_KEEP_THIS_A_SECRRRET                                             = 14259,  -- Oh...but let's keep this a secrrret from Ghanraam, shall we? Otherwise I'll tear your throat out and leave it on my master's doorstep!
        YOU_BRRROUGHT_ONE_I_ALWAYS_KNEW_YOU_HAD                                       = 14260,  -- You brrrought one! I always knew you had a killer instinct. Now, how about I keep it warm for you?
        HAND_IT_OVER_MIGHT_AS_WELL_I_D                                                = 14261,  -- Hand it over? Might as well. I'd rather not.
        THANKS_I_LL_MAKE_SURE_TO_KEEP_IT                                              = 14262,  -- Thanks! I'll make sure to keep it in purrrfect condition for you!
        FINE_I_RRRESPECT_THAT_YOU_DON_T_WANT                                          = 14263,  -- Fine, I rrrespect that you don't want to live under the cat's foot...but see if I ever take anything you bring me again!
        MORE_FOR_ME_ER_YOU_ALRRRIGHT_THEN                                             = 14264,  -- # more for me--er, you? Alrrright then.
        I_KNEW_YOU_D_BRING_ME_A_LOT                                                   = 14265,  -- I knew you'd bring me a lot of these arrrtifacts, but this is ridiculous! There's not a whisker of room left to store them!
        MY_MY_MY_LOOK_WHAT_THE_CAT_DRAGGED                                            = 14266,  -- My, my, my, look what the cat dragged in. I'd be happy to rrreconstruct this for you...under one condition.
        I_PRRROMISE_I_WON_T_LEAVE_ANY_MARKS                                           = 14267,  -- I prrromise I won't leave any marks...so what do you say?
        AGREE_TO_HER_TERMS_I_VE_NO_OTHER                                              = 14268,  -- Agree to her terms? I've no other choice. Never!
        GOOD_KITTY_NOW_I_LL_NEED_A_FEW                                                = 14269,  -- Good kitty! Now, I'll need a few % to get this prrrocess started.
        TO_RRRESTORE_YOU_LL_NEED_TO_BRING_ME                                          = 14270,  -- To rrrestore %, you'll need to bring me # . Oh, and I'll also be taking # as compensation for my suffering. Got it?
        ALSO_YOU_DIDN_T_HAPPEN_TO_RRRECEIVE_ANYTHING                                  = 14271,  -- Also...you didn't happen to rrreceive anything from that scumbag Ghanraam, did you? Well, there's more than one way to skin a cat--if you did, things are going to get a little prrricey.
        DON_T_GO_DOWN_WITHOUT_A_FIGHT_OH                                              = 14272,  -- Don't go down without a fight! Oh, and can I have all your materrrials if you die?
        IN_ADDITION_TO_I_RRREQUIRE_AND_AS_COMPENSATION                                = 14273,  -- In addition to %, I rrrequire...# and # as compensation for my suffering.
        IN_ADDITION_TO_AND_I_RRREQUIRE_AND_AS                                         = 14274,  -- In addition to % and %, I rrrequire...# and # as compensation for my suffering.
        IT_S_PRRROBABLY_NOT_THE_CAT_S_MEOW                                            = 14275,  -- It's prrrobably not the cat's meow, but it's good enough, right?
        EXCHANGE_ITEMS_YES_NO                                                         = 14276,  -- Exchange items? Yes. No.
        THANKS_3                                                                      = 14277,  -- Thanks!
        HERE_S_YOUR_RRREWARD_SUGARPELT_I_DIDN_T                                       = 14278,  -- Here's your rrreward, sugarpelt. I didn't want to keep you waiting, so I prrrepared one in advance.
        BRRRING_SOME_MORE_WHEN_YOU_HAVE_THE_TIME                                      = 14279,  -- Brrring some more when you have the time!
        BRRRING_SOME_MORE_WHEN_YOU_HAVE_THE_TIME_2                                    = 14280,  -- Brrring some more when you have the time! (And don't you dare breathe a word of this to Ghanrrraam!)
        I_THOUGHT_MY_FUR_WAS_GONNA_TURN_GRRRAY                                        = 14281,  -- I thought my fur was gonna turn grrray waiting for you, dreamboat.
        THEY_SAY_THAT_KNOWLEDGE_IS_POWER_SO_HOW                                       = 14282,  -- They say that knowledge is power, so how about I overrrpower you with some knowledge, precious paws?
        ABOUT_WHAT_DO_YOU_WISH_TO_KNOW_PLAN                                           = 14283,  -- About what do you wish to know? Plan stock numbers. Ker armor. Sigyn armor. Omodaka armor. Nabu armor. Fea armor. Ares +1 armor. Skadi +1 armor. Usukane +1 armor. Marduk +1 armor. Morrigan +1 armor. Nothing.
        WHICH_PARTS_NONE_OF_THESE_NONE_I_M                                            = 14284,  -- Which parts? %. %. %. %. %. None of these. None, I'm done.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_CHECK_NONE_OF                                             = 14285,  -- What do you want to check? %. %. %. %. %. None of these. None, I'm done.
        I_VE_GOT_MY_PAWS_ON                                                           = 14286,  -- I've got my paws on # .
        FOR_THIS_I_RRREQUIRE_AND_ALSO_I_LL                                            = 14287,  -- For this, I rrrequire...% and # . Also, I'll need # as compensation for my suffering.
        FOR_THIS_I_RRREQUIRE_AND_ALSO_I_LL_2                                          = 14288,  -- For this, I rrrequire...%, %, and # . Also, I'll need # as compensation for my suffering.
        DON_T_KEEP_ME_WAITING_FOR_TOO_LONG                                            = 14289,  -- Don't keep me waiting for too long, loverboy/girl]. And I know my precious % would never betrrray me, but don't go to Ghanraam if you like your head attached to your neck!
        WHAT_DO_YOU_WANT_FRRROM_ME                                                    = 14290,  -- What do you want frrrom me?
        WHAT_DO_YOU_WANT_FROM_HER_SHOW_ME                                             = 14291,  -- What do you want from her? Show me what can be salvaged! Nothing whatsoever.
        YOU_CAN_FIND_THESE_THRRROUGHOUT_THE_FOUR_REMNANTS                             = 14292,  -- You can find these thrrroughout the four remnants. Don't forrrget about the equipment they can modify, either.
        CAN_T_YOU_COUNT_I_SAID_BRRRING_ME                                             = 14293,  -- Can't you count!? I said brrring me # %! All the money and equipment in the world won't matter if you don't have the prrroper amount of %!
        THESE_PLANS_ARE_ALL_GRRREAT_AND_ALL_BUT                                       = 14294,  -- These plans are all grrreat and all, but where's the equipment with which to synthesize them?
        DON_TCHA_THINK_DAT_FURROWED_BROW_AND_COCKED                                   = 14295,  -- Don'tcha think dat furrowed brow and cocked head o' yers escaped me. Yer int'rested in dis chest, ain'tcha? Well, ya gots good right tah be, 'cause even us Gobbies is fascimanated wit' it. It's some sorta myst'ry box salvaged from a shipwreck in da Gugru Blue! Da mysterious part is dat what goes in don't necessarilies come out!
        WHILE_I_MAY_TOUT_ITS_AMAZIN_NESS_DON                                          = 14296,  -- While I may tout its amazin'ness, don'tcha think fer even a second dat I's at liberty tah divulge hows we came by it. Still, I likes yer face. It's a kind face, one dat says ya won't stabs me in da back, which is more'n I can say fer my own mum. Lemme shows ya how to use dis myst'ry box.
        BAH_DAH_BAH_DAHM_DAH_DAAAHM_YA_OPEN                                           = 14297,  -- Bah-dah-bah-dahm dah-daaahm! Ya open da chest. Dat's it. And da kicker be dat I'm da one doin' da openin'. Ya just gets tah stand dere gawkin' in astonishmament. Easy gig, no?
        OH_YEAH_FORE_I_FORGET_WHAT_GOOD_S                                             = 14298,  -- Oh yeah, 'fore I forget. What good's a chest if ya ain't gots da key? Well, da key to dis chest is da fine art o' waitin'.
        YA_WANTSA_KNOW_DA_HOWS_N_DA_WHYS                                              = 14299,  -- Ya wantsa know da hows n' da whys? Well da bosses had our tinkers tinkerin' on troo' da night and dey foun' dat...
        WELL_DEY_FOUN_DAT_WE_REALLY_GOTS_NO                                           = 14300,  -- Well, dey foun' dat we really gots no idea why da loot changes. Anywho, ya's wanna wait 'n wait 'n wait, den keep on waitin' some more. "Good things come tah dose who wait," right? Well, da longer ya wait, da gooder da thing...maybe. Ya just never know wit' a myst'ry box.
        ALSO_I_CALLS_DA_AMOUNT_O_TIME_YA                                              = 14301,  -- Also, I calls da amount o' time ya's waited yer circa...circama...circamadamian...ugh, yer daily tally. It ain't just da name dat's catchy, though. Da higher yer tally, da gooder yer goods get! Can't get much good--er, simpler dan dat.
        FINALLY_YA_OPENS_DA_CHEST_OOOH_I_CAN                                          = 14302,  -- Finally, ya opens da chest. Oooh, I can barely contain m'self thinkin' o' all da riches I--er, ya could have!
        OH_DAT_S_RIGHT_HEYHEYHEY_GOT_ANY_ITEMS                                        = 14303,  -- Oh, dat's right! Heyheyhey, got any items ya won't be needin'? If so, fork 'em over 'n yer daily tally'll increase! Mebbe not by much, but dat's better'n nothin', am I right?
        AND_DERE_S_NO_BETTER_FEELIN_DAN_TAKIN                                         = 14304,  -- And dere's no better feelin' dan takin' trash and turnin' it into treasure. It's pramactically a new kind o' alchemy! But don't go gung ho 'n overfills da thing 'til its hinges break. Myst'ry boxes don't grow on goobbues, y'know.
        PLUS_I_LL_BE_HERE_TAH_STOPS_YA                                                = 14305,  -- Plus, I'll be here tah stops ya if I sees ya stuffin' whole Gobbiebags worth o' possessions in dere, so don't worry yer oversized noggin' over and over over it. Whats was I sayin' again? Ugh, never mind.
        SADLY_HOWSEVER_ANODDA_MYST_RY_BOUT_DIS_CHEST                                  = 14306,  -- Sadly, howsever, anodda myst'ry 'bout dis chest is dat it won't takes just any ol' bauble. It has da taste o' a picky peiste--it feasts upon nothin' but da rarest and unique-est o' artifacts.
        LASTLY_SINCE_WE_DON_T_KNOWS_WHERE_DA                                          = 14307,  -- Lastly, since we don't knows where da items go once inside, ya ain't gettin' nothin' back datcha put in. Ya reap whatcha sow, and da weather ain't always condusimasive to a good harvest, am I right? My condolemances in advance for any losses ya mights incur from da myst'ry box's fickle nature.
        DAT_ALL_MAKE_NOUGH_SENSE_TAH_YA_JUST                                          = 14308,  -- Dat all make 'nough sense tah ya? Just say da woid when ya wanna use my services. I's more'n happy tah help.
        HEY_I_REM_MBER_SEEIN_YER_FOICE_ROUND                                          = 14309,  -- Hey! I rem'mber seein' yer foice 'round here. Take a looksie. I's taken' it upon myself tah jigger 'round wit' dese all-new myst'ry boxes, found straight from an ol' capsized vessel in the Gugru Blue.
        I_S_NEVAH_GONNA_SAY_HOW_WE_GOTS                                               = 14310,  -- I's nevah gonna say how we gots our hands on 'em, so dun even ask! But, still, I gots tah say dat dese're somet'in' special! Now try yer hand 'fore I smack ya!
